# .gitignore for SummitEthic Ansible Infrastructure

### Vault & Sensitive Files ###
# Never commit your vault password file or unencrypted secrets!
.vault_pass
vault/secrets.yml
secrets.yml.dec

### Ansible Temporary & Cache Files ###
# Ignore Ansible's temporary files and local fact cache.
*.retry
*.log
ansible-facts-cache/
/tmp/ansible-*
*.vault

### Downloaded Roles & Collections ###
# Ignore roles and collections managed by ansible-galaxy.
# The requirements.yml file should be committed instead.
.ansible/
roles/geerlingguy.*

### Python ###
# Ignore Python virtual environments and cache files.
.venv/
venv/
env/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

### Editor & IDE Directories ###
# Ignore local editor configuration.
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

### Generated Files & Logs ###
# Ignore generated reports, logs, and other artifacts.
*.xml
*.html
*.json
coverage/
test-results/
dependency-check-report.*
license_report.html
deployment-record.json
/tree
audit.log
*.log

### OS-specific ###
# Ignore macOS and Windows system files.
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
